column2: title
column8: description

column2: MAVEN Ancillary Bundle
column8: A bundle that contains MAVEN data return files from Electrical Power System; Guidance, Navigation and Control, NGMIS Instrument Data; Particle and Fields Instrument; Periapsis Timing Estimator; Remote Sensing (IUVS) Instrument; Solar Array Switching Modules; Universal Switching Modules and Inertial Measurement Unit. It also include mission events including events from the MAVEN Payload Operations Center events database, and MAVEN science events.

column2: MAVEN Electrical Power System Data Return Files (DRF) Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Electrical Power System Data Return Files (DRFs).

column2: MAVEN Guidance Navigation and Control Data Return Files (DRF) Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Guidance, Navigation and Control Data Return Files (DRFs).

column2: MAVEN Neutral Gas and Ion Mass Spectrometer (NGIMS) instrument Data Return Files (DRF) Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Neutral Gas and Ion Mass Spectrometer (NGIMS) Instrument Data Return Files (DRFs).

column2: MAVEN Particle and Fields instrument Data Return Files (DRF) Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Particle and Fields Instrument Data Return Files (DRFs).

column2: MAVEN Periapsis Timing Estimator Data Return Files (DRF) Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Periapsis Timing Estimator Data Return Files (DRFs).

column2: MAVEN Remote Sensing (IUVS) instrument Data Return Files (DRF) Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Remote Sensing (IUVS) Instrument Data Return Files (DRFs).

column2: MAVEN Solar Array Switch Module 1 Data Return Files (DRF) Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Solar Array Switching Module 1 Data Return Files (DRFs).

column2: MAVEN Solar Array Switch Module 2 Data Return Files (DRF) Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Solar Array Switching Module 2 Data Return Files (DRFs).

column2: MAVEN Solar Array Switch Module 3 Data Return Files (DRF) Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Solar Array Switching Module 3 Data Return Files (DRFs).

column2: MAVEN Universal Switching Module 1 Data Return Files (DRF) Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Universal Switching Module 1 Data Return Files (DRFs).

column2: MAVEN Universal Switching Module 2 Data Return Files (DRF) Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Universal Switching Module 1 Data Return Files (DRFs).

column2: MAVEN Universal Switching Module 3 Data Return Files (DRF) Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Universal Switching Module 1 Data Return Files (DRFs).

column2: MAVEN Universal Switching Module 4 Data Return Files (DRF) Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Universal Switching Module 1 Data Return Files (DRFs).

column2: MAVEN Universal Switching Module 5 Data Return Files (DRF) Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Universal Switching Module 1 Data Return Files (DRFs).

column2: MAVEN Universal Switching Module 6 Data Return Files (DRF) Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Universal Switching Module 1 Data Return Files (DRFs).

column2: MAVEN Events List Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN mission events file including events from the MAVEN Payload Operations Center events database, and MAVEN science events.

column2: MAVEN Intertial Measurement Unit Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Inertial Measurement Unit Data Return Files (DRFs).

column2: MAVEN Extreme ultraviolet (EUV) Calibrated Data Bundle
column8: A bundle containing MAVEN Extreme ultraviolet (EUV) calibrated irradiances in each of the three instrument bandpasses (Watts/m**2).

column2: MAVEN Extreme ultraviolet (EUV) calibrated irradiances Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Extreme ultraviolet (EUV) calibrated irradiances in each of the three instrument bandpasses (Watts/m**2).

column2: MAVEN Extreme ultraviolet (EUV) Modelled Data Bundle
column8: A bundle containing MAVEN Extreme ultraviolet (EUV) modeled minute-averaged irradiance in units of Watts/m**2/nm.

column2: MAVEN Extreme ultraviolet (EUV) daily averaged modelled irradiance spectra Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Extreme ultraviolet (EUV) Modeled minute-averaged irradiance in units of Watts/m**2/nm

column2: MAVEN Extreme ultraviolet (EUV) minute averaged modelled irradiance spectra Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Extreme ultraviolet (EUV) Modeled daily irradiance in units of Watts/m^2/nm

column2: MAVEN Insitu Key Parameters Data Bundle
column8: A bundle that contains key parameters from the in situ instruments on MAVEN: NGIMS, EUV, LPW, MAG, SEP, STATIC, SWEA, and SWIA. Instrument data is derived directly from Level 2 data. Ephemeris information is derived using SPICE libraries and kernels provided by MAVEN/NAV team and Lockheed-Martin.

column2: MAVEN Insitu Key Parameters Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN key parameters from the in situ instruments on MAVEN: NGIMS, EUV, LPW, MAG, SEP, STATIC, SWEA, and SWIA. Instrument data is derived directly from Level 2 data. Ephemeris information is derived using SPICE libraries and kernels provided by MAVEN/NAV team and Lockheed-Martin.

column2: MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) Calibrated Data Bundle
column8: A bundle that contains fully calibrated, science quality data produced by the MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) instrument. The data include spacecraft potential, electric field waveforms and wave power. The data have been provided by the LPW team in CDF files.

column2: MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) Calibrated Current-Voltage Relationships Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) current-voltage relationships from the voltage sweep on the probes (one sweep every other sub-cycle).

column2: MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) Spacecraft Potential Data Collection
column8: A collection of the MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) spacecraft potential based on all 4 sub-cycles and from both booms merged to one time series. Note that data values of '-nan' can be treated as equivalent to 'nan'.

column2: MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) Low Frequency Electric-Field Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) low frequency electric field measurements from every other sub-cycle

column2: MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) High Frequency Burst Mode Calibrated Electric-Field Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) burst mode high frequency, high amplitued calibrated electric field data from selected time periods

column2: MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) Low Frequency Burst Mode Calibrated Electric-Field Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) burst mode low frequency, high amplitued calibrated electric field data from selected time periods

column2: MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) Medium Frequency Burst Mode Calibrated Electric-Field Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) burst mode medium frequency, high amplitued calibrated electric field data from selected time periods

column2: MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) Calibrated Active Mode Spectra Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) active spectra from 1 out of 4 sub-cycles (active if ping-option is enabled; the three different frequency ranges merged).

column2: MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) Calibrated Passive Mode Spectra Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) passive spectra from 1 out of 4 sub-cycles (active if ping-option is enabled; the three different frequency ranges merged).

column2: MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) Derived Data Bundle
column8: A bundle that contains data which have been derived from other data products or determined by fits to other data. These are science quality data produced by the MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) instrument. The data include densities, temperatures, and Poynting flux. The data have been provided by the LPW team in CDF files.

column2: MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) Derived Electron Temperature Data Collection
column8: A collection of the MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) electron temperature and density derived based on the IV-curves and when available adjusted based on wave derived electron density. Note that data values of '-nan' can be treated as equivalent to 'nan'.

column2: MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) Derived Electron Density Data Collection
column8: A collection of Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) electron density derived from Langmuir line in the Passive/Active spectras.

column2: MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) Raw Data Bundle
column8: A bundle that contains raw uncompressed, uncalibrated data from the MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) telemetry packets. Includes data from active sub-cycle waves, PAS sub-cycle MF, LF and HF waves, Langmuir probe sub-cycle, active DAC read back information, active table read back, housekeeping information including LPW temperatures and voltages, raw Medium Frequency High Speed Burst Mode (HSBM) packet data, and EUV data including EUV temperatures.

column2: MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) Raw Wave Active Sub-Cycle Potentials Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) active Sub-cycle Waves: the potential of each probe (mono-pole), and the potential between the two probes (di-pole).

column2: MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) Active DAC Readback Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) active DAC read back information.

column2: MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) Active Table Readback Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) active table read back, the active tables used for the instrument operation.

column2: MAVEN Raw Extreme ultraviolet (EUV) Packet Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN raw Extreme ultraviolet (EUV) data including EUV temperature.

column2: MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) Raw High Frequency High Speed Burst Mode (HSBM) Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) raw High Frequency High Speed Burst Mode (HSBM) packet data, containing a time history of the potentials between the two probes (dipole). Created only in the Passive sub-cycle.

column2: MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) Raw Low Frequency High Speed Burst Mode (HSBM) Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) raw Low Frequency High Speed Burst Mode (HSBM) packet data, containing a time history of the potentials between the two probes (dipole). Created only in the Passive sub-cycle.

column2: MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) Raw Medium Frequency High Speed Burst Mode (HSBM) Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) raw Medium Frequency High Speed Burst Mode (HSBM) packet data, containing a time history of the potentials between the two probes (dipole). Created only in the Passive sub-cycle.

column2: MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) Housekeeping Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) housekeeping information including LPW temperatures and voltages.

column2: MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) Raw Wave Passive Sub-Cycle Potentials Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) passive Sub-cycle Waves: the potential of each probe (mono-pole), and the potential between the two probes (di-pole).

column2: MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) Raw Wave Active Sub-Cycle Onboard FFT in High Frequency Range Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) ACT Sub-cycle HF Waves: The onboard calculated FFT high frequency bands from ACT (Active) sub-cycle.

column2: MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) Raw Wave Passive Sub-Cycle Onboard FFT in High Frequency Range Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) PAS Sub-cycle HF Waves: The onboard calculated FFT high frequency bands from PAS (Passive) sub-cycle.

column2: MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) Raw Wave Active Sub-Cycle Onboard FFT in Low Frequency Range Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) ACT Sub-cycle LF Waves: The onboard calculated FFT low frequency bands from ACT (Active) sub-cycle.

column2: MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) Raw Wave Passive Sub-Cycle Onboard FFT in Low Frequency Range Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) PAS Sub-cycle LF Waves: The onboard calculated FFT low frequency bands from PAS (Passive) sub-cycle.

column2: MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) Raw Wave Active Sub-Cycle Onboard FFT in Medium Frequency Range Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) ACT Sub-cycle MF Waves: The onboard calculated FFT medium frequency bands from ACT (Active) sub-cycle.

column2: MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) Raw Wave Passive Sub-Cycle Onboard FFT in Medium Frequency Range Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) PAS Sub-cycle MF Waves: The onboard calculated FFT medium frequency bands from PAS (Passive) sub-cycle.

column2: MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) Raw Langmuir Probe Sensor 1 Sub-Cycle Sweep Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) boom 1 Langmuir probe Sub-cycle: the current information from the boom where the potential is swept and the potential from the other probe.

column2: MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) Raw Langmuir Probe Sensor 2 Sub-Cycle Sweep Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Langmuir Probe and Waves (LPW) boom 2 Langmuir probe Sub-cycle: the current information from the boom where the potential is swept and the potential from the other probe.

column2: MAVEN Magnetometer (MAG) Calibrated Data Bundle
column8: A bundle that contains MAVEN Magnetometer (MAG) calibrated vector magnetic field data acquired by the Fluxgate Magnetimeter instrument. The data are expressed in Planetocentric, Sun State and Payload coordinates.

column2: MAVEN Tabulated vector magnetic field vs. time in planetocentric coordinates Data Collection
column8: A collection of vector magnetic field data acquired by the Fluxgate Magnetimeter instrument aboard the MAVEN spacecraft. The data are calibrated and provided in physical units (nT). The time resolution depends on the telemetry rate available when the data were taken. The data are expressed in Planetocentric coordinates.

column2: MAVEN Tabulated vector magnetic field vs. time in payload coordinates Data Collection
column8: A collection of vector magnetic field data acquired by the Fluxgate Magnetimeter instrument aboard the MAVEN spacecraft. The data are calibrated and provided in physical units (nT). The time resolution depends on the telemetry rate available when the data were taken. The data are expressed in Payload coordinates.

column2: MAVEN Tabulated vector magnetic field vs. time in Sun-state coordinates Data Collection
column8: A collection of vector magnetic field data acquired by the Fluxgate Magnetimeter instrument aboard the MAVEN spacecraft. The data are calibrated and provided in physical units (nT). The time resolution depends on the telemetry rate available when the data were taken. The data are expressed in Sun State coordinates.

column2: MAVEN ROSE Calibrated Data Bundle
column8: This bundle contains the predicted and residual frequency received at Earth, and transmitted from Earth.

column2: MAVEN ROSE Sky and Resudual Frequencies Data Collection
column8: Time series of predicted and residual frequency received at Earth.

column2: MAVEN ROSE Derived Data Bundle
column8: This bundle contains electron density profiles derived from frequency residuals during occultations.

column2: MAVEN ROSE Electron Density Profile Data Collection
column8: Vertical profile of electron density and related information.

column2: MAVEN ROSE Raw Data Bundle
column8: This bundle contains raw data concerning the radio signal transmitted from Earth and the radio signal received at Earth, calibration collections containing a prediction for the frequency of the radio signal received at Earth and information on the effects of Earth's ionosphere, troposphere, and weather, and a browse collection contains plots that provide an overview of received data.

column2: MAVEN ROSE Radio Science Receiver (RSR) Data Collection
column8: Radiometric data associated with the radio signal received at Earth by an open-loop receiver. Radio Science Receiver Data File formatted as DSN Radio Science Receiver Standard Formatted Data Unit.

column2: MAVEN ROSE Radio Science Tracking and Navigation File (TNF) Data Collection
column8: Radiometric data associated with the radio signal transmitted from Earth. Tracking and Navigation Service Data File (TNF) formatted as DSN Tracking System Data Archival Format TRK-2-34.

column2: MAVEN Solar Energetic Particle (SEP) Calibrated Data Bundle
column8: A bundle that contains MAVEN Solar Energetic Particle (SEP) calibrated Level 2 science data, as well as the raw count data from which they are derived, and ancillary ephemeris data. The calibrated data are in physical units, and include electron and ion spectra in the 4 look directions (2 look directions for each sensor/file).

column2: MAVEN Solar Energetic Particle (SEP) Ancillary Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Solar Energetic Particle (SEP) ancillary data including supporting ephemeris data useful in the interpretation of the SEP calibrated data.

column2: MAVEN Solar Energetic Particle (SEP) Raw Ion and Electron Counts Data Collection
column8: A collection of raw MAVEN Solar Energetic Particle (SEP) ion and electron counts for each of the 256 particles counters.

column2: MAVEN Solar Energetic Particle (SEP) Calibrated Ion and Electron Spectra Data Collection
column8: A collection of calibrated MAVEN Solar Energetic Particle (SEP) sensor ion and electron spectra.

column2: MAVEN SupraThermal And Thermal Ion Composition (STATIC) Calibrated Data Bundle
column8: A bundle that containts MAVEN SupraThermal And Thermal Ion Composition (STATIC) time-ordered fully calibrated differential energy flux, calibrated fast housekeeping data, time-ordered time-of-flight (TOF) raw data and raw event data. Collections are summed over mass assuming O2+, over look direction, over multiple spins

column2: MAVEN SupraThermal And Thermal Ion Composition (STATIC) Housekeeping Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN SupraThermal And Thermal Ion Composition (STATIC) time-ordered fully calibrated housekeeping data, derived from APID 2a. The 99 different housekeeping data include instrument voltages and currents, configuration bytes, table check sums, etc.

column2: MAVEN SupraThermal And Thermal Ion Composition (STATIC) Calibrated Energy Flux: 64 Energy x 2 Mass Bins Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN SupraThermal And Thermal Ion Composition (STATIC) time-ordered fully calibrated differential energy flux in 64 energy bin x 2 mass bin arrays, summed over look direction. Data are derived from APID c0.

column2: MAVEN SupraThermal And Thermal Ion Composition (STATIC) Calibrated Energy Flux: 32 Energy x 32 Mass Bins Data Collection
column8: This collection contains files with time-ordered fully calibrated differential energy flux in 32 energy bin x 32 mass bin arrays, summed over look direction. Data are derived from APID c2.

column2: MAVEN SupraThermal And Thermal Ion Composition (STATIC) Calibrated Energy Flux: 4 Energy X 64 Mass Bins Data Collection
column8: This collection contains files with time-ordered fully calibrated differential energy flux in 4 energy bin x 64 mass bin arrays, summed over look direction. Data are derived from APID c4.

column2: MAVEN SupraThermal And Thermal Ion Composition (STATIC) Calibrated Energy Flux: 32 Energy X 64 Mass Bins Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN SupraThermal And Thermal Ion Composition (STATIC) time-ordered fully calibrated differential energy flux in 32 energy bin x 64 mass bin arrays, summed over look direction. Data are derived from APID c6.

column2: MAVEN SupraThermal And Thermal Ion Composition (STATIC) Calibrated Energy Flux: 32 Energy X 16 Solid Angle Bins Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN SupraThermal And Thermal Ion Composition (STATIC) time-ordered fully calibrated differential energy flux in 32 energy bin x 16 solid angle bin arrays (16 deflection angles and summed over anodes, but assumed that counts are from anode 7 in the ram direction), summed over mass assuming O2+. Data are derived from APID c8.

column2: MAVEN SupraThermal And Thermal Ion Composition (STATIC) Calibrated Energy Flux: 16 Energy X 64 Solid Angle Bins Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN SupraThermal And Thermal Ion Composition (STATIC) time-ordered fully calibrated differential energy flux in 16 energy bin x 64 solid angle bin arrays (4 deflection angles x 16 anodes), summed over mass assuming O2+. Data are derived from APID ca.

column2: MAVEN SupraThermal And Thermal Ion Composition (STATIC) Calibrated Energy Flux: 32 Energy X 8 Solid Angle X 32 Mass Bins Data Collection
column8: This collection contains files with time-ordered fully calibrated differential energy flux in 32 energy bin x 8 solid angle bin (8 deflection angles and summed over anodes, but assumed that counts are from anode 7 in the ram direction) x 32 mass bin arrays. Data are derived from APID cc.

column2: MAVEN SupraThermal And Thermal Ion Composition (STATIC) Calibrated Energy Flux: 32 Energy X 8 Solid Angle X 32 Mass Bins Data Collection
column8: This collection contains files with time-ordered fully calibrated differential energy flux in 32 energy bin x 8 solid angle bin (8 deflection angles and summed over anodes, but assumed that counts are from anode 7 in the ram direction) x 32 mass bin arrays. Data are derived from APID cd.

column2: MAVEN SupraThermal And Thermal Ion Composition (STATIC) Calibrated Energy Flux: 16 Energy X 64 Solid Angle Bins Data Collection
column8: This collection contains files with time-ordered fully calibrated differential energy flux in 16 energy bin x 64 solid angle bin (4 deflection angles x 16 anodes) x 16 mass bin arrays. Data are derived from APID ce.

column2: MAVEN SupraThermal And Thermal Ion Composition (STATIC) Calibrated Energy Flux: 16 Energy X 64 Solid Angle X 16 Mass Bins Data Collection
column8: This collection contains files with time-ordered fully calibrated differential energy flux in 16 energy bin x 64 solid angle bin (4 deflection angles x 16 anodes) x 16 mass bin arrays. Data are derived from APID cf.

column2: MAVEN SupraThermal And Thermal Ion Composition (STATIC) Calibrated Energy Flux: 16 Energy X 64 Solid Angle X 8 Mass Bins Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN SupraThermal And Thermal Ion Composition (STATIC) time-ordered fully calibrated differential energy flux in 16 energy bin x 64 solid angle bin (4 deflection angles x 16 anodes) x 8 mass bin arrays. Data are derived from APID d0.

column2: MAVEN SupraThermal And Thermal Ion Composition (STATIC) Calibrated Energy Flux: 16 Energy X 64 Solid Angle X 8 Mass Bins Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN SupraThermal And Thermal Ion Composition (STATIC) time-ordered fully calibrated differential energy flux in 16 energy bin x 64 solid angle bin (4 deflection angles x 16 anodes) x 8 mass bin arrays. Data are derived from APID d1.

column2: MAVEN SupraThermal And Thermal Ion Composition (STATIC) Calibrated Energy Flux: 64 Solid Angle X 2 Mass Bins Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN SupraThermal And Thermal Ion Composition (STATIC) time-ordered fully calibrated differential energy flux in 64 solid angle bin (4 deflection x 16 anodes) x 2 mass bin arrays. Data are derived from APID d4.

column2: MAVEN SupraThermal And Thermal Ion Composition (STATIC) Raw Event Data Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN SupraThermal And Thermal Ion Composition (STATIC) time-ordered raw event data. Data are derived from APID d6.

column2: MAVEN SupraThermal And Thermal Ion Composition (STATIC) Fast Housekeeping Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN SupraThermal And Thermal Ion Composition (STATIC) time-ordered fully calibrated fast housekeeping data. Data are derived from APID d7.

column2: MAVEN SupraThermal And Thermal Ion Composition (STATIC) Event Rate Data: 12 Rate Channels Summed Over a Single Spin Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN SupraThermal And Thermal Ion Composition (STATIC) time-ordered event rate data summed over a spin. Data are derived from APID d8.

column2: MAVEN SupraThermal And Thermal Ion Composition (STATIC) Event Rate Data: 12 Rate Channels Summed Over Multiple Spins Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN SupraThermal And Thermal Ion Composition (STATIC) time-ordered event rate data sorted into 12 rates x 64 energy bin arrays that are summed over multiple spins. Data are derived from APID d9.

column2: MAVEN SupraThermal And Thermal Ion Composition (STATIC) Event Rate Data Selected Channel Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN SupraThermal And Thermal Ion Composition (STATIC) time-ordered event rate data from a selected rate channel. Data are derived from APID da

column2: MAVEN SupraThermal And Thermal Ion Composition (STATIC) Raw Time-of-Flight Data Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN SupraThermal And Thermal Ion Composition (STATIC) time-ordered time-of-flight (TOF) raw data. Data are derived from APID db.

column2: MAVEN Solar Wind Electron Analyzer (SWEA) Calibrated Data Bundle
column8: A bundle that contains MAVEN Solar Wind Electron Analyzer (SWEA) electron pitch angle distributions, electron energy/angle (3D) distributions, omni-directional electron energy spectra, electron energy/angle (3D) distributions and electron pitch angle distributions in units of differential energy flux (eV/cm**2 sec ster eV) at the MAVEN archive telemetry rate

column2: MAVEN Solar Wind Electron Analyzer (SWEA) Archive Rate 3D Electron Distributions Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Solar Wind Electron Analyzer (SWEA) electron energy/angle (3D) distributions in units of differential energy flux (eV/cm**2 sec ster eV) at the MAVEN archive telemetry rate.

column2: MAVEN Solar Wind Electron Analyzer (SWEA) Archive Rate Electron Pitch Angle Distributions Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Solar Wind Electron Analyzer (SWEA) electron pitch angle distributions in units of differential energy flux (eV/cm**2 sec ster eV) at the MAVEN archive telemetry rate.

column2: MAVEN Solar Wind Electron Analyzer (SWEA) Survey Rate 3D Electron Distributions Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Solar Wind Electron Analyzer (SWEA) electron energy/angle (3D) distributions in units of differential energy flux (eV/cm**2 sec ster eV) at the MAVEN survey telemetry rate.

column2: MAVEN Solar Wind Electron Analyzer (SWEA) Survey Rate Electron Pitch Angle Distributions Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Solar Wind Electron Analyzer (SWEA) electron pitch angle distributions in units of differential energy flux (eV/cm**2 sec ster eV) at the MAVEN survey telemetry rate.

column2: MAVEN Solar Wind Electron Analyzer (SWEA) Survey Rate Omni-Directional Electron Energy Spectra Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Solar Wind Electron Analyzer (SWEA) omni-directional electron energy spectra in units of differential energy flux (eV/cm**2 sec ster eV) at the MAVEN survey telemetry rate

column2: MAVEN Solar Wind Ion Analyzer (SWIA) Calibrated Data Bundle
column8: A bundle that contains MAVEN Solar Wind Ion Analyzer (SWIA) onboard moment files with time-ordered ion moments converted to physical units and coordinates, as computed onboard from Coarse and Fine ion distributions, as well as fine and course survey 3d files with time-ordered fully calibrated ion distributions in units of differential energy flux derived from the SWIA Fine distribution Survey telemetry

column2: MAVEN Solar Wind Ion Analyzer (SWIA) Calibrated Coarse Archive 3D Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Solar Wind Ion Analyzer (SWIA) coarse archive 3d files with time-ordered fully calibrated ion distributions in units of differential energy flux derived from the SWIA Coarse distribution Archive telemetry, as well as a header of ancillary information needed to interpret the data.

column2: MAVEN Solar Wind Ion Analyzer (SWIA) Calibrated Coarse Survey 3D Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Solar Wind Ion Analyzer (SWIA) coarse survey 3d files with time-ordered fully calibrated ion distributions in units of differential energy flux derived from the SWIA Coarse distribution Survey telemetry, as well as a header of ancillary information needed to interpret the data.

column2: MAVEN Solar Wind Ion Analyzer (SWIA) Calibrated Fine Archive 3D Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Solar Wind Ion Analyzer (SWIA) fine archive 3d files with time-ordered fully calibrated ion distributions in units of differential energy flux derived from the SWIA Fine distribution Archive telemetry, as well as a header of ancillary information needed to interpret the data.

column2: MAVEN Solar Wind Ion Analyzer (SWIA) Calibrated Fine Survey 3D Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Solar Wind Ion Analyzer (SWIA) fine survey 3d files with time-ordered fully calibrated ion distributions in units of differential energy flux derived from the SWIA Fine distribution Survey telemetry, as well as a header of ancillary information needed to interpret the data.

column2: MAVEN Solar Wind Ion Analyzer (SWIA) Calibrated Onboard Survey Moment Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Solar Wind Ion Analyzer (SWIA) onboard moment files with time-ordered ion moments converted to physical units and coordinates, as computed onboard from Coarse and Fine ion distributions, as well as a header with ancillary information needed to interpret the moments.

column2: MAVEN Solar Wind Ion Analyzer (SWIA) Calibrated Onboard Survey Spectra Data Collection
column8: A collection of MAVEN Solar Wind Ion Analyzer (SWIA) onboard spectra files with time-ordered angle-averaged ion energy spectra in units of differential energy flux, as computed onboard from Coarse ion distributions, as well as a header with ancillary information needed to interpret the spectra.
